readable.content: A black dog runs into the ocean next to a pile of seaweed . A black lav runs into the water on the beach , with swimmers in the distance and sea kelp in the foreground . A dog at the shore of an ocean , with seaweed in foreground . A dog is running in the waves at the beach . A pile of seaweed sits on the sand , behind it a big black dog is running in the water .
